{"tid":672664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【幫幫眼】14歲女童馮樂怡 失蹤1個月","createTime":"2018-05-21T07:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T08:30:34.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"62f1b635ecb47ea167bb116fa7513aa1d2fd0e77","tid":672664,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180521/large/1526888418_ca46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180521%2Flarge%2F1526888418_ca46.jpg&h=71f4b26d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n14歲女童馮樂怡於上月22日下午離開油塘油麗邨的住所後便告失蹤，其家人於5日後向警方報案，警方經調查後今日呼籲市民提供失蹤女童的消息。<br />\n<br />\n馮樂怡身高約1.61米，體重約42公斤，瘦身材，尖面型，黃皮膚，蓄長黑直髮。她最後露面時身穿白色印花上衣。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲，任何人如有馮樂怡的消息或曾見過她，請致電3661 0316或電郵至rmpu-ke-2@police.gov.hk與東九龍總區失蹤人口調查組，或與任何一間警署聯絡。"},{"pid":"006a0d85afce8b300d1292de3a9ca43466902e40","tid":672664,"uid":107990,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:05:05.000Z","msg":"5日後先報？"},{"pid":"ac90ae149f00e082406badff077b86dc7ff26e90","tid":672664,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:08:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/160808_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F160808_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7a4d61ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3af80d9c942d6c495e0bb75fbfdcde7c0ab79893","tid":672664,"uid":55488,"like":1,"dislike":39,"score":-38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:12:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"875e11831fc7ed838cbd6fae6414ee5b18cc1969","tid":672664,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"006a0d85afce8b300d1292de3a9ca43466902e40","tid":672664,"uid":107990,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T08:05:05.000Z","msg":"5日後先報？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2